Class GitUtils.TeamscaleGitCredentialsProvider

  • java.lang.Object

  • Enclosing class:
    GitUtils

    public static final class GitUtils.TeamscaleGitCredentialsProvider
extends org.eclipse.jgit.transport.UsernamePasswordCredentialsProvider
    Basic credentials provider for the jgit library that automatically accepts requests whether we trust a source. This must be done, as we have no possibility to ask the user. Additionaly this class carries information about a possible git ssh key that should be used, so that it can later be used for configuration.
